lead_paragraph: Russia's Elena Vesnina, the last unseeded woman standing, has set up her dream last four Wimbledon match with world number one and defending champion Serena Williams and knows she will have to take her chances, few as they may be.

headline.print_headline: Unseeded Vesnina Earns Dream Semi-Final With Serena
